  "detailed_description": "Fight in the Arena is a text-based RPG with turn-based fighting.<br><br>Since your childhood you wanted to be a fighter. Now, you have finally the chance. A sponsor searches for new fighters in your village and hosts a small tournament.<br><br>Defeat your opponents in the arena to become the Indomitable, a title not many fighters hold.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> In-depth Turn-Based Combat<br></li><li> Customize your character<br></li><li> 1-2 hour long experience <br></li><li> Defeat over 30 opponents</li></ul>",
